umes an existing session, the transcript must include all historical messages, not just new ones since the plugin/hook loaded\",\"numLines\":40,\"startLine\":1,\"totalLines\":111}},\"sourceToolAssistantUUID\":\"cb9796fc-b6f0-48f5-b112-64bee7c2fa84\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"6790313f-0341-40ab-8254-13aa4b95f2ef\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/soph/Work/entire/devenv/cli\",\"sessionId\":\"a8533fc6-4167-49d5-9143-32f1d83dd315\",\"version\":\"2.1.17\",\"gitBranch\":\"soph/small-rewind-refactor\",\"slug\":\"calm-brewing-cerf\",\"message\":{\"model\":\"claude-opus-4-5-20251101\",\"id\":\"msg_01GbbDeycqTtF9zUYrfVv322\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"The document now has two core principles:\\n1. Full Transcript Storage\\n2. Native Format PreservationThis captures the user's requirement well. Let me confirm the changes are good.\",\"signature\":\"\"}],\"stop_reason\":null,\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":8,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":788,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":80733,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":788},\"output_tokens\":3,\"service_tier\":\"standard\",\"inference_geo\":\"not_available\"}},\"requestId\":\"req_011CYKDPzxxVadPsC89vpxSa\",\"type\":\"assistant\",\"uuid\":\"38282b46-7baa-42f6-8095-710a75ce5f2a\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-02-20T11:07:32.874Z\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"38282b46-7baa-42f6-8095-710a75ce5f2a\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/soph/Work/entire/devenv/cli\",\"sessionId\":\"a8533fc6-4167-49d5-9143-32f1d83dd315\",\"version\":\"2.1.17\",\"gitBranch\":\"soph/small-rewind-refactor\",\"slug\":\"calm-brewing-cerf\",\"message\":{\"model\":\"claude-opus-4-5-20251101\",\"id\":\"msg_01GbbDeycqTtF9zUYrfVv322\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Added a second core principle section:\\n\\n```markdown\\n## Core Principle: Native Format Preservation\\n\\nStore transcripts in the **agent's native format**. Any transformation or normalization \\nshould only be done to support CLI features (rewind, resume, summarization, file extraction), \\nnot for backend or web UI consumption.\\n\\n**Why:**\\n- The backend/web UI should handle format differences, not the CLI\\n- Transforming for downstream consumers couples the CLI to their requirements\\n- Native formats ensure compatibility with agent's own import/export tools\\n- Reduces risk of data loss from lossy transformations\\n\\n**Do:**\\n- Store the raw transcript as the agent produces it\\n- Parse the native format when CLI features need specific data (e.g., extract file paths for `entire status`)\\n- Let the backend normalize formats for display\\n\\n**Don't:**\\n- Create a \\\"universal transcript format\\\" in the CLI\\n- Transform logs to match what the web UI expects\\n- Strip or restructure data to simplify backend processing\\n```\"}],\"stop_reason\":null,\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":8,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":788,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":80733,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":788},\"output_tokens\":3,\"service_tier\":\"standard\",\"inference_geo\":\"not_available\"}},\"requestId\":\"req_011CYKDPzxxVadPsC89vpxSa\",\"type\":\"assistant\",\"uuid\":\"6e9457db-ff2c-4f51-a9f8-d07658a90297\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-02-20T11:07:34.913Z\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"6e9457db-ff2c-4f51-a9f8-d07658a90297\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/soph/Work/entire/devenv/cli\",\"sessionId\":\"a8533fc6-4167-49d5-9143-32f1d83dd315\",\"version\":\"2.1.17\",\"gitBranch\":\"soph/small-rewind-refactor\",\"slug\":\"calm-brewing-cerf\",\"type\":\"progress\",\"data\":{\"type\":\"hook_progress\",\"hookEvent\":\"Stop\",\"hookName\":\"Stop\",\"command\":\"go run ${CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR}/cmd/entire/main.go hooks claude-code stop\"},\"parentToolUseID\":\"4609ff79-9a21-48